WEBVTT

00:13:29.258 --> 00:13:31.686
u kojoj su ljudi ili veličanstveni heroji

00:13:31.710 --> 00:13:33.318
ili bolesni zlotvori,

00:13:33.342 --> 00:13:36.359
čak iako znamo da to
nije istina o ljudima.

00:13:36.383 --> 00:13:40.369
Ono što je istina je da smo
i jedno i drugo,

00:13:40.393 --> 00:13:43.579
da postoje i sive zone.

00:13:43.603 --> 00:13:46.481
Sjajno je da su društveni mediji dali glas

00:13:46.505 --> 00:13:47.901
ljudima koji ga nisu imali,

00:13:47.925 --> 00:13:50.579
ali sada se kreira društvo nadgledanja

00:13:50.603 --> 00:13:54.953
gde je za samoodržanje
bolje biti bezglasan.

00:13:55.423 --> 00:13:56.856
Nemojmo to dozvoliti.

00:13:56.880 --> 00:13:58.032
Hvala vam.

00:13:58.056 --> 00:14:03.774
(Aplauz)